---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import aboutUs from "../assets/about-us.png";
---

<section
  class="px-6 lg:px-12 py-12 lg:py-16 scroll-fade-in"
>
  <div class="bg-neutral-100 py-8 lg:py-10 px-6 lg:px-10 rounded-lg border border-neutral-200">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-start">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <div
          class="w-full bg-black rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center p-6"
        >
          <Image src="/logo2.svg" alt="About Us" width={400} height={400} class="w-full max-w-[300px] lg:max-w-[400px] h-auto" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h2
          class="text-neutral-900 mb-6 lg:mb-8 text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl"
          style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: -0.04em; line-height: 1.1;"
        >
          ABOUT US
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 lg:space-y-6 text-neutral-800">
          <p
            class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl leading-relaxed"
            style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
          >
            Project Likha is an open, community-driven space for tech
            enthusiasts, programmers, artists, and digital creators who believe
            in learning through sharing. It brings together people from
            different backgrounds to explore, create, and grow through shared
            knowledge.
          </p>
          <p
            class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl leading-relaxed"
            style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-style: normal; letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
          >
            There is no central founder - everyone participates as equals.
            Project Likha blends art and technology, encouraging collaboration
            where creativity meets code and ideas turn into meaningful learning.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
